    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Impressions fron our Father-Son trip to Saariselkä, where we went Fatbiking, Skiing and XC Skiing ❄️☀️</p>

<p><a data-flickr-embed="true" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/hendrikmorkel/50946061547/in/dateposted/" title="Fatbiking in Kiilopää"><img src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/50946061547_f89a529e10_b.jpg" width="1024" height="683" alt="Fatbiking in Kiilopää" /></a><script async="" src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p>

<!-- more -->

<p><strong>Disclosure</strong>: <em>This trip was supported financially by the local Tourism office. As you know: I’m keepin’ it real and tell you how it is - I maintain full editorial control of the content published on Hiking in Finland. Read the <a href="https://hikinginfinland.com/about/">Transparency Disclaimer</a> for more information on affiliate links &amp; blogger transparency.</em></p>

<p><a data-flickr-embed="true" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/hendrikmorkel/50946059177/in/photostream/" title="Northern Lights at the Parking Lot"><img src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/50946059177_aa5b04be21_b.jpg" width="1024" height="683" alt="Northern Lights at the Parking Lot" /></a><script async="" src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p>

<p>Travelling safely during the Covid-19 Pandemic is possible in Finland (with some caveats, more about these <a href="https://twitter.com/hendrikmorkel/status/1361235118329913344">here</a>) and so my 9-year old son and me travelled to <a href="https://www.inarisaariselka.fi/en/">Saariselkä</a> - long-time readers will remember my <a href="https://hikinginfinland.com/2019/10/mountainbiking-in-lapland.html">autumn</a> trip there. Saariselkä is a tranquil little village with 300 inhabitants and lays at the gates of the <a href="https://hikinginfinland.com/2013/09/urho-kekkonen-national-park.html">Urho Kekkonen National Park</a> and <a href="https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLqEBC4yj3Faikt3HHS3jU8l3Fm8pxQvN3">Hammastunturi Wilderness</a>. It has a superb network of Fatbike and XC Skiing trails, a small but very good Ski Resort and plenty of other opportunities of enjoying the outdoors. As well as many great accommodation options, like the wonderful <a href="https://www.laplandhotels.com/EN/hotels-in-lapland/saariselka/lapland-hotels-riekonlinna.html">Lapland Hotels Riekonlinna</a> where we stayed.</p>

<p><a data-flickr-embed="true" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/hendrikmorkel/50945953901/in/photostream/" title="Small man Fast"><img src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/50945953901_4cbb90d668_b.jpg" width="1024" height="683" alt="Small man Fast" /></a><script async="" src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p>

<p><a data-flickr-embed="true" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/hendrikmorkel/50945262543/in/photostream/" title="Winter Trees 2"><img src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/50945262543_6cde7efebb_b.jpg" width="1024" height="683" alt="Winter Trees 2" /></a><script async="" src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p>

<p><a data-flickr-embed="true" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/hendrikmorkel/50945261373/in/photostream/" title="Golden Morning Light on the Ski slopes"><img src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/50945261373_db751a9763_b.jpg" width="1024" height="683" alt="Golden Morning Light on the Ski slopes" /></a><script async="" src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p>

<p>We were exceptionally lucky with the weather - it was ☀️ every day but bitterly cold, some days at low as a felt temperature of -32°C - but even those temps were bearable with the <a href="https://youtu.be/E_ma70A6HkM">right clothes</a> and keeping active!</p>

<p><a data-flickr-embed="true" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/hendrikmorkel/50945262948/in/photostream/" title="Iisakkipää Selfie"><img src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/50945262948_9972d4f2fa_b.jpg" width="1024" height="768" alt="Iisakkipää Selfie" /></a><script async="" src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p>

<p>Enjoy this short visual taster of our trip to Lapland, and stay tuned for the full report and Video coming later this month!</p>

